sentinel.led
Class EventSet

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--sentinel.led.EventSet
class EventSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The EventSet class is used to store a composite event occurrence (a set of ParameterLists) and its associated time stamp. It contains methods to make a union of two or threee composite event occurrences.

union

void union(EventSet s1,
           EventSet s2,
           EventSet s3)
This method forms a union of three event sets s1, s2 and s3. The timestamp of the combined set will be the highest among the timestamps of s1, s2 and s3.
